## â–¶ï¸ How to Run the Translator

### Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/DhirChampaneri/asl-translator.git  
cd asl-translator  

### Install dependencies:
pip install -r requirements.txt  

### Run the real-time translator:
python realtime_predict.py  

A webcam window will appear â€” perform ASL signs to see the predicted letters.

---

## ğŸ§  Model Training

To retrain the model or collect new data:

### Collect new data:
python collect_data.py  

### Train the model:
python train_model.py  

This generates a new asl_letters_model.joblib file.

